    "causal_summary": "The eight shipped CI workflows are all `on: pull_request` with `paths:` filters, and a grep for `schedule:` or `cron:` across `.github/workflows/` returns empty, so no data-quality check runs on a timer or on demand. The change-triggered tiers are blind to three escape classes: a defect in a file the `paths:` filter never matched, a backfill blind spot a one-shot migration left behind, and cross-surface coherence drift between a spec doc and its JSONs that no single-file gate sees.",
